Body:
Sometimes I can read my devices' logs in VS Code, and sometimes I can't. At the beginning of the week I was able to read it, two days ago I stopped receiving the logs, but Iot Hub dashboard was showing that I was receiving them. Today I was able to read it for 2 hours, and than it stopped again ...

My Azure Stream Analytics just receives input streams when I can read logs. Do you have any idea of what is happening here ?

My Iot Hub location is North Europe
